\noun default
\color inherit
\lang british
 
\begin_inset Formula $\iff$
\end_inset


\begin_inset Formula $p_{mod}=0$
\end_inset

) then one can show quite easily that detecting the particle at one hole,
 leads to loss of information about the modular variable! This is at the
 very least now makes some sense in doing.
\begin_inset Newline newline
\end_inset

