\begin_layout Itemize
So Ali described methods to both create a schrodinger cat state and an entangled
 cat state 
\begin_inset Formula $\left|\psi\right\rangle \sim\left|\alpha\right\rangle \left|-\alpha\right\rangle +\left|\alpha\right\rangle \left|-\alpha\right\rangle $
\end_inset


