\begin_layout Itemize
Thought along the lines of displacing states if there existed a number operator
 like object for the coherent state, namely 
\begin_inset Formula $\hat{O}\left|\alpha\right\rangle =\alpha\left|\alpha\right\rangle $
\end_inset

, then I could use this to construct something like 
\begin_inset Formula $D(\lambda)e^{-i\text{Im}[(\lambda\hat{O})]}\left|\bar{\alpha}\right\rangle \propto\left|\bar{\alpha}\right\rangle $
\end_inset

 where 
\begin_inset Formula $\left|\bar{\alpha}\right\rangle =\sum_{n}\left|n\alpha\right\rangle $
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
