\begin_inset Formula $\hat{S}_{\alpha}=\sum_{n}\left|(n+1)\alpha\right\rangle \left\langle n\alpha\right|$
\end_inset

 with 
\begin_inset Formula $\alpha$
\end_inset

 sufficiently large so that 
\begin_inset Formula $\left\langle n\alpha|m\alpha\right\rangle \approx\delta_{nm}$
\end_inset

 .
