\begin_inset Formula $(1-\hat{S}_{\alpha+\lambda})D(\lambda)\left|\bar{\alpha}\right\rangle \propto\left|\bar{\alpha}\right\rangle $
\end_inset

 which for sure won't work because you would need something like 
\begin_inset Formula $\hat{S}_{n\alpha+\lambda}$
\end_inset

 for each term in the summation which defeats the purpose of the operator
 itself.
