\end_deeper
\begin_layout Itemize
However, nothing stops us from considering the Bell states with this formalism,
 because 
\begin_inset Formula $X^{\dagger}$
\end_inset

 and 
\begin_inset Formula $Y^{\dagger}$
\end_inset

 act the same way on 
\begin_inset Formula $\left|\uparrow\right\rangle $
\end_inset

