\begin_layout Itemize
Obtaining the `interference term' for our state: Turns out it is rather
 complicated! It's something like 
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\left\langle p_{1}p_{2}|\Psi'\right\rangle =\frac{1}{\sqrt{2}}\varphi(p_{1})\varphi(p_{2})\sum_{n,m}e^{i(np_{1}+mp_{2})}\frac{L}{\hbar}\left[-\cos\frac{\delta}{2}\left((-)^{m}-(-)^{n}\right)+\sin\frac{\delta}{2}\left(1+(-1)^{n+m}\right)\right]
\]

\end_inset

and trying to simplify this even for 2 slits is not easy where 
\begin_inset Formula $n,m\in\{-1,0\}$
\end_inset

.
\end_layout

